OL,7,FA coroner has concluded the death of a
OL,8,Fretired engineer after a routine
OL,9,Fcancer scan at the Royal Bolton
OL,10,FHospital was due to misadventure
OL,11,Fcontributed to by neglect.
OL,13,FDavid Horsman, 65, of Westhoughton,
OL,14,Fdied on 28 March 2022 after he
OL,15,Fsuffered a cardiac arrest in a mobile
OL,16,FCT scanner unit in the hospital car
OL,17,Fpark.
