OL,7,FConcluding a three-day inquest at
OL,8,FBolton Coroners' Court, Coroner John
OL,9,FPollard said a breakdown in
OL,10,Fcommunication between the radiographer
OL,11,Fconducting the scan and the
OL,12,Fswitchboard operator had led to a
OL,13,Fcritical delay in Mr Horsman being
OL,14,Ftreated in time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
