OL,7,FThe radiographer made three emergency
OL,8,Fcalls to the switchboard after Mr
OL,9,FHorsman had suffered an anaphylactic
OL,10,Freaction to the contrast dye injected
OL,11,Finto him before the scan, but the
OL,12,Fswitchboard operator repeatedly
OL,13,Fmisunderstood the correct location -
OL,14,Feven though it would have been
OL,15,Fdisplayed on her screen.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
