OL,4,Cman's death at hospital after routine
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,FThe crash team which might have saved
OL,8,FMr Horsman's life was sent instead to
OL,9,Fa children's ward and only found Mr
OL,10,FHorsman 17 minutes after the first
OL,11,Fcall. They were able to resuscitate
OL,12,Fhim, but he died the following day.
OL,14,FThe inquest heard independent expert
OL,15,Fmedical evidence that with prompt and
OL,16,Fappropriate care, Mr Horsman's death
OL,17,Fwould probably have been avoided.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/11
