OL,7,FThe coroner said: "The levels, tone
OL,8,Fand effectiveness of these calls were
OL,9,Ffar below what we would accept as a
OL,10,Freasonable standard."
OL,12,FFollowing the conclusion of the
OL,13,Finquest, Mr Horsman's widow Jane said:
OL,14,F"David went to the hospital for a
OL,15,Froutine scan and I stayed home because
OL,16,Fof covid restrictions still in place
OL,17,Fat Royal Bolton Hospital.
OL,19,F"We had no qualms about the procedure
OL,20,Fand spent the time preparing for a
OL,21,Fholiday we were about to take.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/11
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
