OL,4,Cman's death at hospital after routine
OL,5,Cscan
OL,7,F"I was horrified to receive the call
OL,8,Fthat David had had a reaction to the
OL,9,FCT scan procedure, and by the
OL,10,Ffollowing day my world had been tipped
OL,11,Fupside down.
OL,13,F"After David was making a good
OL,14,Frecovery from the bowel cancer three
OL,15,Fyears earlier, his death was
OL,16,Fcompletely unforeseen. To lose him
OL,17,Fwhen we were at the start of our
OL,18,Fretirement has been and continues to
OL,19,Fbe devastating.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/11
