OL,7,F"To hear of the circumstances
OL,8,Fsurrounding David's death, the
OL,9,Ffailings at Royal Bolton Hospital,
OL,10,Fhave sickened me.
OL,12,F"I expected that David would be safe
OL,13,Fand would have trusted the hospital
OL,14,Fstaff to take good care of him if
OL,15,Fsomething went wrong. Something did go
OL,16,Fwrong, but the hospital let David and
OL,17,Fhis family down. I am appalled."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/11
