OL,7,FNegligence specialist Stephen Jones of
OL,8,FLeigh Day solicitors, representing
OL,9,FJane Horsman, said: "Listening to the
OL,10,Fcall recordings being played in court
OL,11,Fand hearing how things went so
OL,12,Ftragically and unnecessarily wrong was
OL,13,Fvery upsetting.
OL,15,F"The process for calling the crash
OL,16,Fteam was quite straightforward but was
OL,17,Fsimply not handled properly.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/11
