OL,7,F"The crash team were reduced to
OL,8,Froaming the hospital to try to locate
OL,9,Fthe emergency, and when they finally
OL,10,Fcame across David it proved to be too
OL,11,Flate to save him. David's death should
OL,12,Fhave been avoided."
OL,14,FThe inquest had heard Mr Horsman was
OL,15,Fbeing routinely scanned after being
OL,16,Fsuccessfuly treated for bowel cancer
OL,17,Fand had never previously suffered a
OL,18,Freaction to being injected with
OL,19,Fcontrast dye.
