OL,7,FDr Francis Andrews, Medical Director
OL,8,Fat Bolton NHS Foundation Trust, said:
OL,9,F"We fully accept the findings of the
OL,10,Finquest and our commitment to the
OL,11,Ffamily and all who knew him is to make
OL,12,Fsure that we learn and do as much as
OL,13,Fwe possibly can to prevent such a
OL,14,Ftragedy from happening again.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/11
