OL,7,F"We no longer commission private
OL,8,Fproviders for radiology services; have
OL,9,Fcontinued to run simulation exercises
OL,10,Frelated to identifying and managing
OL,11,Fanaphylaxis with our existing and new
OL,12,Fradiology staff; and all call handlers
OL,13,Fworking in our switchboard service
OL,14,Fhave taken part in extensive training
OL,15,Fbefore being able to continue in their
OL,16,Froles.
OL,18,F"Nothing we can say or do will take
OL,19,Faway from such a devastating outcome
OL,20,Ffor Mr Horsman's family, and our
OL,21,Fsympathies remain with them."
